{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm a huge believer in hands-on education."},{"time":4000,"text":"But you have to have the right tools."},{"time":6000,"text":"If I'm going to teach my daughter about electronics,"},{"time":9000,"text":"I'm not going to give her a soldering iron."},{"time":11000,"text":"And similarly, she finds prototyping boards"},{"time":13000,"text":"really frustrating for her little hands."},{"time":16000,"text":"So my wonderful student Sam and I"},{"time":19000,"text":"decided to look at the most tangible thing we could think of:"},{"time":21000,"text":"Play-Doh."},{"time":23000,"text":"And so we spent a summer"},{"time":25000,"text":"looking at different Play-Doh recipes."},{"time":27000,"text":"And these recipes probably look really familiar"},{"time":29000,"text":"to any of you who have made homemade play-dough --"},{"time":31000,"text":"pretty standard ingredients you probably have in your kitchen."},{"time":34000,"text":"We have two favorite recipes --"},{"time":36000,"text":"one that has these ingredients"},{"time":38000,"text":"and a second that had sugar instead of salt."},{"time":40000,"text":"And they're great. We can make great little sculptures with these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"But the really cool thing about them is when we put them together."},{"time":46000,"text":"You see that really salty Play-Doh?"},{"time":48000,"text":"Well, it conducts electricity."},{"time":50000,"text":"And this is nothing new."},{"time":52000,"text":"It turns out that regular Play-Doh that you buy at the store conducts electricity,"},{"time":54000,"text":"and high school physics teachers have used that for years."},{"time":57000,"text":"But our homemade play-dough"},{"time":59000,"text":"actually has half the resistance of commercial Play-Doh."},{"time":61000,"text":"And that sugar dough?"},{"time":63000,"text":"Well it's 150 times more resistant to electric current"},{"time":65000,"text":"than that salt dough."},{"time":67000,"text":"So what does that mean?"},{"time":69000,"text":"Well it means if you them together you suddenly have circuits --"},{"time":72000,"text":"circuits that the most creative, tiny, little hands"},{"time":75000,"text":"can build on their own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":83000,"text":"And so I want to do a little demo for you."},{"time":87000,"text":"So if I take this salt dough,"},{"time":89000,"text":"again, it's like the play-dough you probably made as kids,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and I plug it in --"},{"time":93000,"text":"it's a two-lead battery pack, simple battery pack,"},{"time":96000,"text":"you can buy them at Radio Shack"},{"time":98000,"text":"and pretty much anywhere else --"},{"time":100000,"text":"we can actually then"},{"time":103000,"text":"light things up."},{"time":107000,"text":"But if any of you have studied electrical engineering,"},{"time":109000,"text":"we can also create a short circuit."},{"time":111000,"text":"If I push these together, the light turns off."},{"time":114000,"text":"Right, the current wants to run through the play-dough, not through that LED."},{"time":116000,"text":"If I separate them again, I have some light."},{"time":118000,"text":"Well now if I take that sugar dough,"},{"time":120000,"text":"the sugar dough doesn't want to conduct electricity."},{"time":122000,"text":"It's like a wall to the electricity."},{"time":124000,"text":"If I place that between, now all the dough is touching,"},{"time":127000,"text":"but if I stick that light back in,"},{"time":129000,"text":"I have light."},{"time":131000,"text":"In fact, I could even add some movement to my sculptures."},{"time":134000,"text":"If I want a spinning tail, let's grab a motor,"},{"time":136000,"text":"put some play-dough on it, stick it on"},{"time":139000,"text":"and we have spinning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"And once you have the basics,"},{"time":147000,"text":"we can make a slightly more complicated circuit."},{"time":149000,"text":"We call this our sushi circuit. It's very popular with kids."},{"time":152000,"text":"I plug in again the power to it."},{"time":155000,"text":"And now I can start talking about parallel and series circuits."},{"time":158000,"text":"I can start plugging in lots of lights."},{"time":163000,"text":"And we can start talking about things like electrical load."},{"time":166000,"text":"What happens if I put in lots of lights"},{"time":168000,"text":"and then add a motor?"},{"time":170000,"text":"It'll dim."},{"time":172000,"text":"We can even add microprocessors"},{"time":175000,"text":"and have this as an input"},{"time":177000,"text":"and create squishy sound music that we've done."},{"time":180000,"text":"You could do parallel and series circuits"},{"time":182000,"text":"for kids using this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"So this is all in your home kitchen."},{"time":188000,"text":"We've actually tried to turn it into an electrical engineering lab."},{"time":191000,"text":"We have a website, it's all there. These are the home recipes."},{"time":194000,"text":"We've got some videos. You can make them yourselves."},{"time":196000,"text":"And it's been really fun since we put them up to see where these have gone."},{"time":199000,"text":"We've had a mom in Utah who used them with her kids,"},{"time":201000,"text":"to a science researcher in the U.K.,"},{"time":203000,"text":"and curriculum developers in Hawaii."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"So I would encourage you all to grab some Play-Doh,"},{"time":208000,"text":"grab some salt, grab some sugar and start playing."},{"time":211000,"text":"We don't usually think of our kitchen as an electrical engineering lab"},{"time":214000,"text":"or little kids as circuit designers,"},{"time":216000,"text":"but maybe we should."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"Have fun. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}